Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.33,0:00:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once it starts moving, it never stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today we tackle the truth behind a mysterious key.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A shocking trick in a locked room!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing the one and only truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.50,0:00:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has the appearance of a child, and the brain of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the Hikari Maison apartments?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... It's probably been condemned by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:52.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, could it be this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Light Maison.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:01:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Underwater Key in the Locked Room Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I remodeled the apartments earlier this spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no idea. It really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is completely different from\Nwhen you were studying as a student, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:24.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was on a whim that I even lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And because your parents kept meddling in your business,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You ran off six months later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you live here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My children all grew up and moved away long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I do have one grandson living with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:54.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's great that you're not lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. His name's Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:03:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He studies architecture at Jounan University.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But recently, he's been locking\Nhimself up in his room for hours on end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I keep asking him why, but he won't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I thought that a famous\Ndetective like you might be able to make him talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why you called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he'd be here about eight o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My grandson and I live on the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:29.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I rent out the first through third floors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll just use the spare key.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. He's my grandson, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really! What a dirty child!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahh! What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:04.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's only crayon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's even on the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An Underwater Monument.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a key in the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto! Hang on, Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto! Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The vein in his left arm's been slit open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No other knife marks in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quick! Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know! Call Kido-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kido-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a medical student and lives just below us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a friend of Makoto's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But your grandson is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kido-san! Kido-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kido-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kido-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kido-san... Something smells!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great. He must have gotten drunk and fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kido-san, Makoto-san had an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wha... Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deceased is Souda Makoto-san, age 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a senior architecture student at Jounan University.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death was a severed vein\Nin the left arm and excessive blood loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the stiffness of his neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably been dead for two or three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which makes the estimated time of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around six or seven o'clock in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, this was a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? A suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Please come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a model that Makoto made.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:48.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a key in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door can only be opened by a special key.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it can't be easily duplicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:08:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The spare keys are kept by his\Ngrandmother and the security company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was the lock when you arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:07.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That makes this a locked room case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why it can be determined to be suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto would never commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I brought him juice this afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even said he wanted to eat pumpkin for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what time was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was about five PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:34.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And while I was gone, Makoto was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what kind of juice was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made it myself to prevent dehydration. It's a special blend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The main ingredients are honey, garlic and banana juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, there were never any signs,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Makoto had suicidal tendencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto was really stressed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He said the model he was making\Nfor his graduation wasn't going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he was depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just look at the messy crayon\Ndrawings and the setup of the apartment itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was surely emotionally disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the white stuff on this key?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whaa!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aww... Look what you did! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's toilet paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toilet paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It could be tissue or some other paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But tissue doesn't melt like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My guess it is toilet tissue cut into strips, then made into string.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he put it on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know. He did have some weird habits, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably just some hobby of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, this is a locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The air vent's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think really think someone\Ncould get through a gap that small?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look here. It's only 15 millimeters long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the other windows are locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which makes this a locked room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't you think it's weird that he committed suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be nearly impossible to cut your vein in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the dark...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were any of the lights on when you came in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... Maybe the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:46.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I turned it on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death is\Nabout six to seven o'clock in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was still daylight outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there aren't any windows in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without some kind of light, there's no\Nway he could have cut his vein open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the criminal turned off the lights after the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if it was a murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal probably did those crayon drawings, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then there's the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did the criminal put the key in the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still have two other questions to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of the same random drawings he did on the walls,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did the criminal carefully\Ncolor in that line on the door post?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And... That window.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it were darker outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to imagine that the criminal didn't notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The window wasn't the only thing that was open!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:53.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I take back what I said. This was a murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:12:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key to this mysterious trick is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This mail box slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, the criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Linked a string to the model.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then pulled it to the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:13.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He drew it through the opening in the mail slot,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then used the key to lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:19.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, he put the key back on the string,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And kept stretching the string.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key moved slowly back into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When it reached the water in the model,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wet toilet tissue broke, and it dropped into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the mystery's been solved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see now. I should have known you'd figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle, there's something I don't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to turn left from the\Nentrance to get to the living room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you drew a string from here to that room,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it pass over the doorjamb and leave a mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the criminal used crayon to mark the doorjamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to make sure that people\Nknew he didn't use string to commit the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And here, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. Right. Now I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal put the key straight into the mail slot and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No trace there, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The air vent. He did the string trick using the air vent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's certainly possible that he tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? You see that dog there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a good watchdog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He barks at everyone but family members.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:13:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Kido-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:02.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He always barks at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's wide open in that yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone was acting weird out there, he'd bark even louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't the air vent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it really was suicide, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. This was a murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim only had one wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are no other signs of injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just one very accurate and deep incision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only person who could do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is someone who has medical knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what trick did he use?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bug trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on. That sweater by the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crayon all over the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And... That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why that window's slightly open.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a halfway locked room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now for the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be something. There's gotta be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's coming from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this cup the one you used for the juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Makoto actually washed the cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've found the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know the trick the criminal used.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma, can I borrow the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot! How could you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Son, you just need the key, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, just what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, Grandma. When I go out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:35.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make sure the lights are off like they were before, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna start now, so everyone be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like something fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A beetle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a male beetle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bug trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's it. That's how the criminal did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did the beetle do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The top of the model is covered with a scent male beetles love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what about that sweater it ran across?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal put his sweater on the floor\Nso that the beetle could walk through easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Floor tiles are hard for beetles to walk across.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hallway and the living room are carpeted, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which made it convenient for the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun, you're incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:02.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. That beetle... Where'd you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! I took it from Kido-san's place. He's got tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry one got away, Kido-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kido-san, before I came and got you\Nearlier, had you already come up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm sure. Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I was just wondering why your\Nhandkerchief smelled like Grandmas homemade juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma brought the juice around five PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kido-san, you took the cup that\NMakoto-san drank from and washed it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then you used your handkerchief\Nto wipe up some that spilled on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:20:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, you were scared that the male beetle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would take one whiff of that strong-smelling juice,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And forget about the scent you'd put on the model tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You rubbed a female beetle's scent\Nall over the top of the model, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kido-kun! Don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take out your handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so stoked that my plan succeeded,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I forgot to deal with the handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had a few drinks to celebrate, and I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you kill Makoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About a year ago, he had this idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That we steal some sedatives from the university and sell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then later, he said he changed his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that you'd be coming tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:21:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got freaked about what would happen if he leaked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Makoto-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Truly regretted what he'd done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably why he decided to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although it's a little late to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:23.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man's life is more precious than you can ever imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can keep thinking about that all the while you're in jail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think long and hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's cost you a big part of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poor Mitsue-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.76,0:23:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It won't make up for losing Makoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.14,0:23:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you two should go visit her once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.68,0:23:21.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you were really terrific tonight, Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.73,0:23:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was nothing. I'm always\Nhearing Uncles deductions, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.48,0:23:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that's something to be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to me, you're learning\Ndetective skills without even trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.33,0:23:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle, you're the one who needs to\Nlearn more about solving mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.55,0:23:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arrest the suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.63,0:23:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Find them! Find Sato and Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:23:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, if we're gonna find any witnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.14,0:24:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should start investigating at that pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't... Don't tell me this place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.52,0:24:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You-know-who lives here, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.98,0:24:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.28,0:24:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Metropolitan Police Officer Love Story 2 (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.07,0:24:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.37,0:24:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor Agasa's new invention
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.35,0:24:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The next chapter is "Love Story 2."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.90,0:24:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}About me and Officer Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.50,0:24:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll rip that hat off your bald head!
